WEBVTT

01:43.090 --> 01:46.060
[[Love Song in Winter]]

01:46.110 --> 01:49.110
[Episode 20]

01:50.140 --> 01:51.240
Don't hurt the hostage.

01:59.410 --> 02:00.530
L-Look at me.

02:01.100 --> 02:02.580
I don't have a weapon.

02:04.640 --> 02:05.750
I'll trade with him, okay?

02:06.510 --> 02:08.070
I'll be the hostage. I'll go with you.

02:10.789 --> 02:11.640
Okay.

02:11.790 --> 02:12.250
Okay.

02:12.470 --> 02:13.140
We're not exchanging.

02:17.910 --> 02:19.030
You won't be able to leave like this.

02:20.990 --> 02:22.210
How about I drive for you?

02:22.710 --> 02:24.160
I'll drive you to wherever you want to go.

02:28.150 --> 02:28.850
Okay?

02:39.910 --> 02:40.740
Don't be nervous.

02:41.640 --> 02:42.350
Yu Zheng.

02:47.020 --> 02:47.720
Get up!

02:49.430 --> 02:49.900
Get up!

02:49.950 --> 02:50.829
Qin Yue, Qin Yue, Qin Yue.

02:50.870 --> 02:51.530
Scatter.

03:00.470 --> 03:00.950
Go.

03:17.340 --> 03:18.329
Open the door.

03:33.660 --> 03:34.430
Go up.

03:45.750 --> 03:46.150
Don't move!

03:46.170 --> 03:46.640
Don't move!

03:53.070 --> 03:53.980
Come on. Let's go.

03:57.190 --> 03:57.820
Take him away.

04:13.470 --> 04:14.710
I really didn't expect this.

04:15.190 --> 04:16.470
A young girl like her

04:16.670 --> 04:17.790
killed two people

04:17.820 --> 04:19.070
and even stabbed a cop.

04:19.610 --> 04:21.269
Don't judge a book by its cover.

04:24.430 --> 04:25.430
Tell me. What's your name?

04:30.780 --> 04:31.860
I'm asking you a question.

04:34.870 --> 04:35.940
If you don't want to say it,

04:36.070 --> 04:36.909
I'll say it for you.

04:38.430 --> 04:39.580
Name, Li Ruonan.

04:39.909 --> 04:40.909
Born on December 30,

04:40.950 --> 04:42.020
1997,

04:42.430 --> 04:43.490
in Chengzhou.

04:44.650 --> 04:45.520
Your family was poor

04:45.550 --> 04:47.310
and your father passed away early.

04:47.430 --> 04:48.740
So you and mother

04:48.950 --> 04:49.670
depended on each other.

05:00.560 --> 05:02.530
You were sent to a martial arts academy ten years ago

05:02.720 --> 05:04.100
but your grades were not good.

05:04.360 --> 05:06.220
and you didn't make any much progress in school.

05:06.430 --> 05:08.480
So you dropped out and wandered around the country,

05:08.790 --> 05:10.110
working part-time jobs for a living.

05:11.150 --> 05:12.230
Until three years ago,

05:12.350 --> 05:13.940
you appeared in Ninghai.

05:14.670 --> 05:15.760
You have no permanent residence,

05:15.790 --> 05:16.750
so you helped others

05:16.830 --> 05:18.660
deal with some special issues

05:18.910 --> 05:20.090
and even started to kill.

05:27.700 --> 05:28.620
Li Ruonan,

05:29.510 --> 05:31.490
have you ever thought about

05:32.110 --> 05:33.670
what kind of sentence

05:33.740 --> 05:34.950
you might receive

05:34.980 --> 05:36.950
if all these issues are combined?

05:43.110 --> 05:43.750
We

05:45.040 --> 05:45.830
are the only ones

05:45.830 --> 05:46.950
that can help you.

05:48.430 --> 05:50.150
I hope you can actively cooperate

05:50.950 --> 05:52.880
and strive to achieve significant meritorious service.

05:54.590 --> 05:55.590
Tell me, why did you kill them?

05:59.120 --> 06:00.340
Who did I kill?

06:01.690 --> 06:02.600
Li Ruonan.

06:02.790 --> 06:03.510
You wouldn't think

06:03.510 --> 06:04.430
we're trying to trick you, would you?

06:04.830 --> 06:06.480
Without enough evidence,

06:06.830 --> 06:08.070
do you think we can bring you here?

06:09.030 --> 06:09.590
Based on the evidence we currently have,

06:09.590 --> 06:10.980
it is sufficient to prove that

06:11.070 --> 06:11.990
you committed the murder of

06:12.030 --> 06:13.310
Wang Qianqian and Ding Jing.

06:14.070 --> 06:15.810
Even if you don't say anything now,

06:15.910 --> 06:17.230
you can't be cleared of suspicion.

06:18.070 --> 06:19.110
Who is Wang Qianqian?

06:21.670 --> 06:22.850
And who is Ding Jing?

06:26.190 --> 06:27.030
Do you think the police

06:27.070 --> 06:28.070
are merely decoration?

06:38.820 --> 06:40.050
There's no use asking like this,

06:40.270 --> 06:41.110
we won't get a confession.

06:47.100 --> 06:48.909
[Li Ruonan] [Mother] [Antisocial personality]

06:55.680 --> 06:56.310
Senior.

07:04.310 --> 07:05.560
Li Ruonan.

07:08.950 --> 07:09.910
There's no point for you

07:09.910 --> 07:10.800
to deny the allegations.

07:10.830 --> 07:11.470
You know that right?

07:12.050 --> 07:13.650
The evidence is solid.

07:14.030 --> 07:15.000
Wouldn't it be better to

07:15.030 --> 07:16.340
give yourself a chance at a reduced sentence?

07:17.190 --> 07:18.420
Wouldn't it be better to strive for an early release

07:18.870 --> 07:19.910
so you get to visit home

07:19.950 --> 07:21.390
and spend more time with your family?

07:23.630 --> 07:24.670
I don't have a family.

07:29.230 --> 07:30.670
Aren't you from Chengzhou?

07:31.940 --> 07:33.450
Your mother is still in your hometown, right?

07:33.550 --> 07:35.310
I said I don't have a family.

07:46.890 --> 07:48.240
You're still young.

07:48.260 --> 07:49.190
What are you doing this for?

07:50.950 --> 07:53.450
What's the point of

07:53.720 --> 07:54.880
shouldering these things alone?

07:56.430 --> 07:57.350
Now that

07:57.670 --> 07:58.630
you're in jail,

07:59.470 --> 08:01.090
to the people out there,

08:01.190 --> 08:02.510
you have only risks

08:02.510 --> 08:03.790
and no value.

08:04.510 --> 08:06.070
Are you executing a paid task

08:06.190 --> 08:07.070
or

08:07.390 --> 08:08.350
are you being threatened?

08:09.510 --> 08:10.710
If you did for money,

08:11.140 --> 08:11.950
that's easy.

08:12.390 --> 08:13.990
You've received the money and done your job.

08:14.390 --> 08:15.440
Now that you're arrested,

08:15.470 --> 08:16.470
you should just tell us.

08:19.270 --> 08:19.960
Let's say

08:19.990 --> 08:21.110
you're being threatened,

08:22.240 --> 08:23.950
you should hurry and tell us what happened

08:24.130 --> 08:25.410
so we can provide your help

08:25.830 --> 08:26.710
to solve your problem.

08:27.430 --> 08:27.950
So great is that?

08:35.780 --> 08:36.559
Fine.

08:39.480 --> 08:40.669
Come back and ask me

08:40.669 --> 08:41.429
once you've investigated the truth.

09:00.670 --> 09:02.360
I've been a policeman for so many years.

09:02.990 --> 09:03.590
I've never seen

09:03.590 --> 09:04.510
a criminal like her.

09:07.670 --> 09:10.440
Stubborn, cold-blooded and scheming.

09:10.670 --> 09:12.080
Admits her crime

09:12.110 --> 09:13.760
and doesn't leave a way out for herself.

09:15.070 --> 09:16.790
A typical antisocial personality.

09:17.310 --> 09:18.960
When I interrogated her

09:19.150 --> 09:20.110
and mentioned her mother,

09:21.590 --> 09:23.380
I can see that although she is very restrained,

09:24.430 --> 09:25.510
deep down,

09:25.990 --> 09:26.950
she is very agitated.

09:31.550 --> 09:32.710
Let's find a breakthrough

09:32.790 --> 09:33.550
through her mother.

09:34.550 --> 09:35.260
Captain Jiang,

09:35.390 --> 09:36.440
based on the information

09:36.470 --> 09:37.550
I've got,

09:37.670 --> 09:38.510
Li Ruonan and Deng Man

09:38.550 --> 09:39.550
shouldn't have had any interactions.

09:40.710 --> 09:42.150
I agree.

09:45.120 --> 09:45.990
How about Ding Jing?

09:46.020 --> 09:46.660
Neither do they.

09:50.510 --> 09:52.320
Senior, what should we do next?

09:53.670 --> 09:54.190
Yiming.

09:55.870 --> 09:57.240
Contact people

09:57.260 --> 09:58.380
from her hometown.

09:58.920 --> 10:00.710
Find out where her mother is now.

10:00.760 --> 10:01.270
Understood.

10:01.700 --> 10:02.340
Qin Yue.

10:02.850 --> 10:04.700
Before Li Ruonan was arrested,

10:04.870 --> 10:06.990
she was looking for something in Ding Jing's house.

10:07.470 --> 10:08.750
Go check the CCTV

10:09.110 --> 10:09.840
and see if anyone went in and out

10:09.860 --> 10:10.700
before and after the incident.

10:11.010 --> 10:11.950
Also,

10:11.970 --> 10:12.730
find out

10:12.960 --> 10:14.050
what exactly is she looking for.

10:14.220 --> 10:14.750
Sure.

10:18.490 --> 10:19.060
Sihan

10:19.960 --> 10:21.050
Keep an eye out.

10:21.170 --> 10:23.300
Find out who were the people

10:23.750 --> 10:24.710
Ding Jing were in contact with

10:24.730 --> 10:25.490
before the murder.

10:26.190 --> 10:26.750
Got it.

10:30.670 --> 10:31.190
Professor Yu,

10:32.160 --> 10:34.380
let's work overtime tonight

10:35.270 --> 10:36.470
to investigate Li Ruonan's

10:36.470 --> 10:37.350
movement trajectory.

10:37.520 --> 10:38.880
See if we can estimate

10:38.910 --> 10:40.010
where she lives.

10:41.040 --> 10:41.900
Got it.

10:42.030 --> 10:43.060
We'll follow your orders.

11:17.100 --> 11:19.060
[Remember to eat!]

11:26.940 --> 11:30.400
[Legal Affairs Office]

11:28.270 --> 11:28.980
Professor Yu.

11:36.360 --> 11:37.190
Breakfast.

11:51.990 --> 11:58.440
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

11:59.990 --> 12:00.520
Senior.

12:02.910 --> 12:03.710
Lower your voice.

12:04.050 --> 12:05.990
He didn't sleep the whole night.

12:07.290 --> 12:08.950
Have you found Li Ruonan's address?

12:08.980 --> 12:10.220
Not yet.

12:11.170 --> 12:11.980
How is it?

12:14.790 --> 12:15.550
Any news?

12:15.730 --> 12:16.470
No.

12:16.590 --> 12:17.430
They went to her house

12:17.450 --> 12:18.410
and found nothing.

12:21.850 --> 12:22.710
How about the CCTV?

12:26.060 --> 12:27.420
I checked the CCTV.

12:27.630 --> 12:28.390
There's nothing much suspicious

12:28.410 --> 12:29.790
other than one person.

12:30.270 --> 12:31.000
Who?

12:33.960 --> 12:40.750
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

12:43.560 --> 12:44.320
Half a month ago,

12:44.350 --> 12:45.750
Dr. Lu went to Ding Jing's house.

12:53.360 --> 12:54.550
But I checked.

12:54.580 --> 12:56.250
Dr. Lu didn't go in.

12:56.350 --> 12:58.100
She was just strolling around at the entrance,

12:58.270 --> 12:59.710
looking like she's searching for something

12:59.710 --> 13:00.630
or ensuring something.

13:07.700 --> 13:08.390
Okay.

13:08.910 --> 13:09.560
Captain Jiang,

13:13.350 --> 13:14.360
we visited

13:14.390 --> 13:15.510
the staff of Ding Jing's company again.

13:15.810 --> 13:16.680
They told us that

13:16.700 --> 13:18.180
someone had made a scene

13:18.870 --> 13:19.750
at the arts seminar.

13:19.870 --> 13:20.910
They played a video

13:20.930 --> 13:21.930
as well as a voice recording.

13:22.370 --> 13:23.200
What video?

13:23.350 --> 13:24.280
They didn't tell us

13:24.310 --> 13:25.410
the details.

13:25.510 --> 13:26.360
It should be a video of

13:26.390 --> 13:27.390
Ding Jing bullying other people.

13:28.210 --> 13:29.330
But on that day,

13:29.520 --> 13:31.200
Ding Jing and Dr. Lu

13:31.250 --> 13:32.200
had an argument.

13:40.490 --> 13:41.200
Here.

13:46.890 --> 13:47.530
Go on with your work.

13:51.470 --> 13:54.660
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

14:12.970 --> 14:15.030
[Nurses' Station]

14:13.940 --> 14:15.170
Why are you here?

14:15.690 --> 14:17.480
Are you here to see Liu Hao?

14:18.120 --> 14:18.950
I’m here to pick you up.

14:19.900 --> 14:20.700
Pick me up?

14:21.610 --> 14:22.940
Hasn't it

14:23.190 --> 14:24.460
just turned twelve o'clock?

14:25.870 --> 14:26.970
I'll wait for you.

14:27.520 --> 14:29.140
Then wait for me at my desk.

14:29.160 --> 14:30.490
No, I'll wait here.

14:32.680 --> 14:33.380
Go ahead with your work.

14:35.390 --> 14:36.060
Well,

14:36.250 --> 14:37.380
I'll go in first then.

15:13.350 --> 15:13.870
You...

15:15.480 --> 15:16.380
What's wrong?

15:16.670 --> 15:17.590
Is there any problem

15:17.590 --> 15:18.950
with your case?

15:19.640 --> 15:20.300
No.

15:24.150 --> 15:25.270
It's quite good today that

15:25.310 --> 15:26.860
you can go home so early.

15:28.380 --> 15:29.640
What do you want to eat?

15:29.660 --> 15:31.340
We could go out and eat too.

15:34.670 --> 15:35.350
Let's go home.

15:59.560 --> 16:01.070
Do you want some water?

16:02.590 --> 16:03.470
No need.

16:05.040 --> 16:05.750
Then,

16:06.110 --> 16:07.070
I'll order a takeout?

16:07.980 --> 16:08.750
We can have that.

16:11.290 --> 16:12.050
Lu Yan,

16:16.720 --> 16:18.210
do you have anything you're hiding from me?

16:25.790 --> 16:27.080
Whether is it

16:27.360 --> 16:28.430
from the past

16:28.460 --> 16:29.720
or the present,

16:30.120 --> 16:31.000
is there nothing?

16:34.030 --> 16:35.070
Why are you

16:35.340 --> 16:36.770
saying this?

16:38.680 --> 16:39.580
Is there?

16:40.510 --> 16:42.490
I'm not hiding anything from you.

16:49.470 --> 16:50.800
I've never been able to understand.

16:54.030 --> 16:55.340
Since eight years ago

16:55.850 --> 16:57.170
when we broke up,

16:58.690 --> 17:00.050
you have never told me the reason,

17:00.940 --> 17:02.150
even up till this day.

17:03.790 --> 17:04.920
So many years have passed,

17:05.960 --> 17:07.040
we've met again

17:08.640 --> 17:09.829
and have been spending time together.

17:11.930 --> 17:13.420
Even when you've had an accident, you refuse to tell me

17:13.450 --> 17:14.490
and continue to hide from me.

17:18.490 --> 17:19.480
I don't understand.

17:20.619 --> 17:21.720
Do you think

17:22.329 --> 17:23.980
I won't face it with you?

17:25.109 --> 17:25.720
Or

17:25.740 --> 17:26.930
you don't trust me at all?

17:30.190 --> 17:31.030
I just...

17:35.420 --> 17:36.640
I just think I should

17:36.670 --> 17:37.820
let bygones be bygones.

17:39.920 --> 17:40.970
I don't want to mention them anymore.

17:52.020 --> 17:52.670
Fine.

17:57.140 --> 17:58.860
Is there a direct connection

18:01.500 --> 18:03.200
between the butterfly hairpin in your box

18:04.110 --> 18:05.500
and your visit to Ding Jing's house?

18:06.790 --> 18:07.270
Also,

18:07.300 --> 18:09.190
was the voice recording at Ding Jing's seminar

18:10.570 --> 18:11.610
done by you?

18:15.550 --> 18:16.630
I don't want to talk about this.

18:18.360 --> 18:19.140
Lu Yan.

18:28.620 --> 18:30.230
The clues are pointing to you.

18:33.640 --> 18:34.980
I don't want you to take the wrong path.

18:42.750 --> 18:43.830
I've been taking the wrong path,

18:43.830 --> 18:44.630
haven't I?

18:46.390 --> 18:48.330
I never told you this.

18:50.270 --> 18:51.110
Deng Man...

18:54.000 --> 18:54.990
Deng Man told me years ago that

18:55.030 --> 18:56.390
you're the person she likes.

18:56.780 --> 18:58.200
I investigated Ding Jing because

18:58.230 --> 18:59.550
I want to know if Deng Man's death

18:59.550 --> 19:01.270
has anything to do with us.

19:03.240 --> 19:04.670
What's the connection between her liking me

19:06.010 --> 19:07.450
and her suicide?

19:08.440 --> 19:09.890
I always thought

19:11.050 --> 19:11.790
the reason why

19:11.820 --> 19:13.030
she committed suicide

19:13.050 --> 19:13.880
was because

19:14.090 --> 19:15.130
she couldn't be with you.

19:15.910 --> 19:17.030
Before she committed suicide,

19:17.110 --> 19:18.390
she asked to meet up with me.

19:18.480 --> 19:19.700
She begged me

19:20.070 --> 19:21.050
to break up with you

19:21.070 --> 19:22.270
for her to be with you.

19:22.300 --> 19:23.670
I didn't agree,

19:23.870 --> 19:25.690
and then she died.

19:27.690 --> 19:28.720
Jiang Chengyi.

19:31.540 --> 19:32.390
Do you know Deng Man

19:32.420 --> 19:34.100
was my best friend?

19:37.860 --> 19:38.960
Her suicide note

19:38.980 --> 19:40.910
was full of words blaming me.

19:42.680 --> 19:43.960
I don't know how to

19:44.000 --> 19:45.150
continue seeing you.

19:47.700 --> 19:48.790
I always thought

19:48.830 --> 19:50.470
my words were

19:50.470 --> 19:51.870
what caused Deng Man

19:51.890 --> 19:53.180
to commit suicide.

19:53.730 --> 19:55.080
I want to get over it.

19:56.320 --> 19:58.320
I want to be with you properly.

20:00.750 --> 20:02.560
We meet again after eight years.

20:02.580 --> 20:03.020
I...

20:04.190 --> 20:05.690
Like you said,

20:06.550 --> 20:07.630
you don't want there to be

20:07.670 --> 20:08.670
any barriers between us.

20:08.690 --> 20:09.860
I think the barrier between us

20:09.890 --> 20:10.810
is exactly this.

20:20.910 --> 20:21.860
Jiang Chengyi.

20:30.840 --> 20:31.870
For the past eight years,

20:31.870 --> 20:33.310
I've been missing you.

20:34.460 --> 20:35.630
But I really don't know

20:35.660 --> 20:36.990
how to be with you.

20:38.200 --> 20:39.150
So I want to remove

20:39.150 --> 20:40.710
this thorn between us.

20:41.660 --> 20:43.030
I want us to have no barriers

20:43.070 --> 20:43.630
nor misunderstandings

20:43.680 --> 20:45.030
and be together properly.

20:46.800 --> 20:48.500
I also want to say that

20:49.710 --> 20:50.630
these eight years

20:52.570 --> 20:54.020
have been hard on you

20:59.370 --> 21:00.220
I'm sorry for that.

21:07.800 --> 21:09.000
So,

21:12.070 --> 21:13.390
you were investigating Ding Jing

21:16.890 --> 21:19.010
in order to prove that Deng Man's death

21:20.430 --> 21:21.860
has nothing to do with us.

21:22.560 --> 21:23.280
Yes.

21:27.890 --> 21:29.890
I don't want to lose you again.

21:31.510 --> 21:33.320
I don't want to run away anymore,

21:34.890 --> 21:35.730
because...

21:36.960 --> 21:37.720
Because of what?

21:41.410 --> 21:42.870
Because I love you.

21:46.560 --> 21:47.550
I want to resolve

21:47.590 --> 21:48.640
all of our misunderstandings.

21:48.720 --> 21:49.480
I want to remove

21:49.510 --> 21:50.550
the thorns between us.

21:50.570 --> 21:52.360
I want to be with you properly.

22:59.350 --> 23:00.150
Honey.

23:00.550 --> 23:01.350
You're up.

23:01.550 --> 23:02.430
Come.

23:02.450 --> 23:03.250
Have a glass of orange juice.

23:03.280 --> 23:04.620
Replenish some Vitamin C.

23:05.100 --> 23:05.870
I can't drink

23:05.910 --> 23:06.830
such cold drinks today.

23:06.950 --> 23:07.760
What's wrong?

23:08.290 --> 23:09.220
Is your period here.

23:11.390 --> 23:11.990
Zhong.

23:12.460 --> 23:13.330
I have a gift for you.

23:18.630 --> 23:20.120
There's a gift for me early in the morning?

23:21.150 --> 23:22.160
What is it, honey?

23:22.190 --> 23:23.010
Open it yourself.

23:30.920 --> 23:31.680
No way.

23:31.710 --> 23:32.610
It's real.

23:32.940 --> 23:33.700
You caught a cold?

23:33.870 --> 23:34.700
I'll get you some medicine.

23:34.720 --> 23:35.550
Come back!

23:37.000 --> 23:37.880
Are your eyes there

23:37.950 --> 23:39.260
to breathe?

23:39.280 --> 23:40.360
Zhong Wenxuan.

23:40.450 --> 23:41.880
What does that mean?

23:42.230 --> 23:43.680
It's a pregnancy test stick.

23:45.620 --> 23:47.220
I'm really worried that

23:47.220 --> 23:48.800
my child's IQ will resemble yours.

23:50.520 --> 23:51.480
You're pregnant?

23:51.860 --> 23:53.070
I'm going to be a father!

23:53.530 --> 23:54.980
That's great, honey!

23:56.700 --> 23:57.720
Don't move.

23:58.290 --> 23:59.070
Honey.

23:59.460 --> 24:00.490
I'm so sorry.

24:00.510 --> 24:01.840
You are now a key protection target.

24:02.960 --> 24:04.080
I just got pregnant.

24:04.110 --> 24:05.070
I'm not that delicate.

24:05.090 --> 24:05.880
Well,

24:06.020 --> 24:07.190
I'll tell Wen Peng that

24:07.210 --> 24:08.650
I won't go to see him this afternoon.

24:08.670 --> 24:09.750
We'll visit the hospital

24:09.770 --> 24:10.590
for a checkup,

24:10.740 --> 24:12.160
and then, go get

24:12.190 --> 24:13.150
some baby products.

24:13.790 --> 24:14.860
I also need to go to the bookstore.

24:14.890 --> 24:16.010
What for?

24:16.070 --> 24:17.110
To get a copy of the Cihai.

24:17.170 --> 24:18.580
We need it to name the baby.

24:21.980 --> 24:22.920
I don't want the study anymore.

24:23.110 --> 24:23.650
Let's demolish it.

24:23.760 --> 24:24.700
Build a baby's room instead.

24:25.040 --> 24:26.130
I don't want these anymore.

24:26.160 --> 24:27.060
Move them to the office.

24:27.160 --> 24:27.890
Let's turn it into

24:27.930 --> 24:29.210
our baby's game room.

24:29.400 --> 24:29.920
No.

24:30.440 --> 24:31.460
Let's not demolish anything.

24:31.500 --> 24:32.350
Let's not demolish anything.

24:32.510 --> 24:33.480
Let's move into a villa.

24:33.500 --> 24:34.100
Buy a bigger house.

24:34.150 --> 24:34.830
Enough, enough.

24:34.860 --> 24:35.340
Stop.

24:35.850 --> 24:37.180
Zhong,

24:37.460 --> 24:39.090
don't make such a fuss.

24:39.110 --> 24:39.720
Alright?

24:39.750 --> 24:40.880
There's no rush.

24:40.910 --> 24:42.030
The child's registration can only be done

24:42.110 --> 24:43.150
when they're more than seven weeks old.

24:43.170 --> 24:43.710
Besides,

24:43.750 --> 24:44.590
we have nine months

24:44.670 --> 24:46.110
to buy slowly things for the baby.

24:46.270 --> 24:46.910
Also,

24:46.950 --> 24:47.790
this house is big enough.

24:47.830 --> 24:48.820
There's no need to change.

24:49.100 --> 24:50.660
I have other plans today.

24:51.150 --> 24:51.790
I'll listen to you, wifey.

24:51.810 --> 24:52.470
Wait.

24:53.190 --> 24:54.290
Why do you still have plans?

24:54.410 --> 24:54.890
Yes.

24:54.920 --> 24:56.640
You should follow your plan,

24:56.750 --> 24:57.270
and then,

24:57.290 --> 24:59.320
send me to Lu Yan's house on your way.

24:59.350 --> 25:00.430
I want to tell her

25:00.470 --> 25:00.950
this good news

25:00.990 --> 25:02.200
and celebrate with her.

25:03.070 --> 25:04.280
Yes, honey.

25:05.680 --> 25:07.300
Shouldn't you celebrate with me?

25:07.330 --> 25:08.980
Why are you celebrating with Lu Yan?

25:09.510 --> 25:11.310
Who is the child's father?

25:51.400 --> 25:52.410
Hang in there.

25:52.990 --> 25:53.610
Come on.

25:56.510 --> 25:57.050
What's wrong?

25:57.590 --> 25:58.210
What's wrong?

25:58.410 --> 25:59.230
You sprained your ankle?

26:02.230 --> 26:03.160
Get on the chair.

26:03.190 --> 26:03.670
Let's go.

26:09.910 --> 26:10.650
Sit.

26:11.840 --> 26:12.660
This foot?

26:12.790 --> 26:13.810
I think so.

26:13.860 --> 26:14.710
Let me see.

26:20.410 --> 26:21.280
Does it hurt here?

26:21.600 --> 26:22.350
Yes.

26:22.920 --> 26:23.720
You sprained the outer side.

26:24.310 --> 26:25.250
You shouldn't rub it.

26:25.280 --> 26:26.340
Go back and apply an ice pack.

26:30.500 --> 26:31.470
There's still a distance

26:31.510 --> 26:32.710
from here to the campus.

26:36.560 --> 26:37.250
How about this?

26:37.290 --> 26:38.350
Wait for me for a while.

26:40.510 --> 26:41.930
Where are you going?

26:48.730 --> 26:50.150
Senior Wen.

26:50.370 --> 26:52.010
Is your back seat

26:52.380 --> 26:53.690
installed separately?

26:53.780 --> 26:54.460
Yes.

26:55.910 --> 26:57.680
Is it for your girlfriend?

26:57.920 --> 26:58.720
It's not.

26:58.870 --> 27:00.580
It's for Zhong.

27:00.720 --> 27:03.450
Does Senior Zhong not own a bike?

27:03.880 --> 27:05.310
If he's riding a bike,

27:05.350 --> 27:06.800
how can he have breakfast in the morning?

27:08.660 --> 27:09.490
Senior.

27:11.470 --> 27:13.740
Do you have a girlfriend?

27:15.860 --> 27:16.480
I don't.

27:20.600 --> 27:21.430
What's wrong?

27:21.850 --> 27:22.970
There's a pit over there.

27:36.010 --> 27:37.240
Has your ankle recovered?

27:41.150 --> 27:42.000
Thank you.

27:42.160 --> 27:43.170
It's much better now.

27:43.600 --> 27:45.300
Don't rub it tonight.

27:45.400 --> 27:46.880
I'll bring you some medicine tomorrow.

27:52.040 --> 27:53.340
See, the textbook is right.

27:53.370 --> 27:55.250
Exercising helps to secrete dopamine

27:55.310 --> 27:56.270
and make people feel happy.

27:56.700 --> 27:57.710
Are you stupid?

27:57.830 --> 27:58.840
This is obviously happiness

27:58.870 --> 28:00.030
brought by a man.

28:02.470 --> 28:03.370
Lu Yan.

28:03.550 --> 28:04.400
Lu Yan.

28:05.810 --> 28:06.670
You heard it.

28:07.200 --> 28:08.990
Leniency to those who confess, severity to those who resist.

28:09.020 --> 28:10.110
What's the progress of

28:10.110 --> 28:10.750
your relationship with Jiang Chengyi?

28:11.010 --> 28:12.110
What do you mean?

28:12.590 --> 28:13.550
Don't see everyone in that light

28:13.570 --> 28:14.690
once you and Zhong got together.

28:14.720 --> 28:16.000
There's...

28:16.500 --> 28:17.640
There's nothing between us.

28:17.820 --> 28:18.680
Yan, tell me.

28:18.700 --> 28:19.730
Are you interested in

28:19.760 --> 28:20.340
Jiang Chengyi?

28:24.070 --> 28:25.870
No.

28:25.920 --> 28:27.450
He just gave me

28:27.550 --> 28:29.820
an ice pack as my senior.

28:30.110 --> 28:32.970
Why are you smiling so widely if there's nothing?

28:33.540 --> 28:34.170
Alright.

28:34.530 --> 28:35.180
I admit it.

28:35.290 --> 28:36.000
Just a little.

28:36.020 --> 28:36.820
-Just...
-A little?

28:36.820 --> 28:37.270
A little.

28:37.310 --> 28:38.350
Isn't it this much now?

28:38.440 --> 28:39.510
Is this considered a little?

28:39.630 --> 28:40.320
That's not true.

28:41.050 --> 28:42.740
What are you going to do next?

28:43.150 --> 28:43.880
Next?

28:43.990 --> 28:44.910
You two now have

28:44.960 --> 28:46.270
mutual feelings.

28:46.470 --> 28:47.190
Shouldn't you confess

28:47.230 --> 28:48.420
and move forward?

28:48.750 --> 28:50.160
Moreover, Ding Jing

28:50.200 --> 28:51.390
is still eyeing him.

28:51.680 --> 28:52.260
Oh, right!

28:52.280 --> 28:53.150
Ding Jing!

28:53.230 --> 28:54.280
I heard that

28:54.310 --> 28:56.160
she and Jiang Chengyi grew up together.

28:56.410 --> 28:57.350
They're childhood sweethearts.

28:58.090 --> 29:00.300
You have to take the lead.

29:00.920 --> 29:03.030
What do you mean by taking the lead?

29:03.470 --> 29:04.790
It's to take the initiative.

29:04.810 --> 29:06.180
What do you mean by taking the initiative?

29:06.350 --> 29:07.560
Let me raise an example.

29:07.590 --> 29:08.070
Like

29:08.190 --> 29:09.100
Zhong and I...

29:29.950 --> 29:31.000
This is

29:31.420 --> 29:32.590
a medicinal wine made by my dad.

29:33.640 --> 29:34.750
For sprains like yours,

29:34.770 --> 29:35.820
apply for a few times and it'll recover.

29:36.420 --> 29:37.110
Thank you.

29:54.120 --> 29:54.720
You...

29:55.400 --> 29:56.820
You need to...

29:58.390 --> 29:59.060
You have to...

30:02.320 --> 30:03.700
You need to rub it harder.

30:04.820 --> 30:05.340
Come.

30:13.700 --> 30:16.660
You need to use more strength.

30:17.210 --> 30:19.190
Otherwise, the bruise inside

30:19.210 --> 30:20.010
won't fade.

30:31.040 --> 30:32.620
Do you always get injured?

30:32.650 --> 30:34.480
That's why you carry medicinal wine with you

30:35.100 --> 30:35.770
all the time?

30:36.270 --> 30:36.870
No.

30:37.220 --> 30:38.610
I went home to get it.

30:41.060 --> 30:42.230
Did you go back

30:42.230 --> 30:43.200
specially for me?

30:43.620 --> 30:45.260
You got hurt while running with me.

30:45.670 --> 30:47.010
I have to be responsible for you.

30:55.470 --> 30:56.550
I mean...

30:57.120 --> 30:58.350
I mean this.

31:13.480 --> 31:14.520
Jiang Chengyi.

31:16.410 --> 31:17.470
I like you.

31:23.680 --> 31:25.120
Do you feel the same way?

31:29.550 --> 31:31.540
Would you be my boyfriend?

31:50.790 --> 31:51.690
I...

31:55.800 --> 31:56.660
I'm sorry.

32:00.720 --> 32:02.100
For what?

32:04.890 --> 32:05.810
It's nothing.

32:10.070 --> 32:11.750
Aren't you nice to me

32:11.770 --> 32:13.130
because you like me?

32:17.930 --> 32:19.140
No, I...

32:19.540 --> 32:20.910
I treat everyone well.

32:34.160 --> 32:34.960
Lu Yan,

32:35.560 --> 32:36.840
I think you can understand.

32:37.390 --> 32:38.550
Now, I can

32:38.990 --> 32:40.230
jog with you

32:40.250 --> 32:41.020
and exercise with you.

32:44.120 --> 32:45.720
But I can't be with you forever.

32:50.110 --> 32:51.320
I don't understand.

32:57.600 --> 32:59.330
I just want an answer.

33:01.620 --> 33:02.370
You...

33:04.810 --> 33:05.670
Do you

33:05.710 --> 33:06.580
not like me at all?

33:10.990 --> 33:11.520
Yes.

33:12.860 --> 33:13.620
I...

33:15.000 --> 33:15.940
don't like you.

34:38.860 --> 34:40.179
[Criminal Investigation Science]

34:50.989 --> 34:51.860
Lu Yan.

35:22.420 --> 35:23.830
[Alarm]

35:31.620 --> 35:32.570
You're awake.

35:34.050 --> 35:35.200
Get some more sleep.

35:53.350 --> 35:54.110
I'll get the door.

36:01.450 --> 36:02.590
There's no sound in there.

36:05.500 --> 36:06.210
Zhong.

36:06.240 --> 36:06.960
Come in.

36:17.360 --> 36:18.410
You're up.

36:18.440 --> 36:20.070
You guys talk. I'll go wash my face.

36:24.440 --> 36:25.480
Looks like

36:26.190 --> 36:28.330
we're not the only ones with good news.

36:29.450 --> 36:30.390
He...

36:31.120 --> 36:32.930
I'll go get him

36:32.950 --> 36:33.550
a toothbrush

36:33.990 --> 36:35.110
holder.

36:40.130 --> 36:41.110
Congratulations.

36:41.130 --> 36:42.290
You're going to be a father.

36:43.560 --> 36:45.010
Thank you.

36:45.020 --> 36:46.550
Aren't you back together too?

36:46.800 --> 36:47.650
It's not easy.

36:47.690 --> 36:48.630
I'm happy for you.

36:53.580 --> 36:55.060
You have to hurry up

36:55.080 --> 36:56.320
and speed up the progress.

36:56.630 --> 36:58.350
If our families give birth to a boy and a girl,

36:58.370 --> 36:59.410
we should arrange an early betrothal.

36:59.870 --> 37:01.560
If they were two girls,

37:01.590 --> 37:02.780
they can be sworn sisters.

37:02.990 --> 37:03.880
If they were two boys,

37:03.900 --> 37:04.690
they are like us,

37:04.970 --> 37:05.940
not brothers

37:05.970 --> 37:07.000
but closer than real brothers.

37:08.360 --> 37:09.250
What era is it?

37:09.280 --> 37:10.210
Arranged betrothal?

37:11.680 --> 37:12.790
What's wrong?

37:13.130 --> 37:14.160
Are you shy?

37:14.980 --> 37:16.490
Isn't it reasonable?

37:16.550 --> 37:17.870
You two like kids too.

37:18.210 --> 37:18.980
This matter

37:19.070 --> 37:19.670
is in no hurry.

37:20.570 --> 37:22.110
Let me

37:22.150 --> 37:24.090
have my romantic life with just the two of us first.

37:26.250 --> 37:27.010
I understand.

37:27.590 --> 37:28.550
You've missed eight years.

37:29.670 --> 37:31.090
You've been counting the days.

37:31.350 --> 37:32.070
It's not easy.

37:35.880 --> 37:37.870
How did it work?

37:39.900 --> 37:41.820
I didn't really...

37:42.040 --> 37:43.500
Say it exactly.

37:44.680 --> 37:45.610
You didn't confess?

37:48.360 --> 37:49.690
Probably...

37:49.710 --> 37:50.190
Not.

37:51.840 --> 37:52.940
That doesn't work.

37:53.690 --> 37:55.510
A piece of advice

37:55.560 --> 37:56.310
from a married man.

37:57.310 --> 37:58.720
Life needs a sense of ritual.

37:59.220 --> 38:00.760
If you don't say anything now,

38:01.080 --> 38:01.990
you'll suffer in the future.

38:03.300 --> 38:04.450
Learn from me.

38:06.120 --> 38:06.670
The food is boiling.

38:06.890 --> 38:07.390
Hurry.

38:08.500 --> 38:09.870
I'll put the broccoli in it.

38:17.550 --> 38:18.510
What?

38:18.990 --> 38:21.050
You agreed without him confessing to you?

38:22.390 --> 38:23.320
Jie.

38:23.340 --> 38:24.500
We are...

38:24.530 --> 38:25.170
No, no, no.

38:25.440 --> 38:26.250
It's not that I don't agree with

38:26.280 --> 38:27.520
you two getting back together.

38:27.550 --> 38:28.830
I don't agree with

38:28.830 --> 38:30.010
you two getting back together casually.

38:30.250 --> 38:31.850
Have you forgotten?

38:31.930 --> 38:33.000
When you first confessed to him,

38:33.030 --> 38:34.070
he turned you down.

38:34.810 --> 38:37.640
You were the one who pursued him ten years ago.

38:37.670 --> 38:38.710
If you don't want him

38:38.750 --> 38:39.430
to do something now,

38:39.450 --> 38:40.260
the chance for him to do it in the future is even lower.

38:41.300 --> 38:43.480
I don't care about being ceremonial.

38:43.510 --> 38:44.150
Besides,

38:44.280 --> 38:46.190
it's not the first time

38:46.230 --> 38:47.140
we got together.

38:47.350 --> 38:48.950
Haven't you heard that saying?

38:48.970 --> 38:50.870
People live for a few moments.

38:51.090 --> 38:52.330
We have to make every moment

38:52.360 --> 38:53.680
more meaningful.

38:54.260 --> 38:55.840
I didn't care about being ceremonial before.

38:56.100 --> 38:57.800
I didn't even want to hold a wedding.

38:58.090 --> 38:59.910
But Zhong does.

39:00.350 --> 39:01.400
Now that I think about it,

39:01.470 --> 39:02.500
I realized

39:02.530 --> 39:03.960
these senses of ritual

39:03.990 --> 39:05.460
are what make our ordinary life

39:05.480 --> 39:06.790
more interesting

39:07.100 --> 39:08.580
and spiced up our relationship.

39:09.330 --> 39:10.870
Zhong treats you so well

39:10.900 --> 39:12.490
but you still pick on him all the time.

39:13.180 --> 39:14.530
Why are you talking about me again?

39:14.560 --> 39:16.640
I'm talking about you now.

39:17.600 --> 39:18.540
Dr. Lu.

39:18.620 --> 39:19.460
Please adopt the right attitude

39:19.480 --> 39:20.900
this time.

39:21.070 --> 39:22.490
Don’t be soft-hearted

39:22.520 --> 39:23.640
whenever you face Jiang Chengyi.

39:23.780 --> 39:25.690
You should at least

39:25.720 --> 39:27.040
let him properly pursue you once.

39:28.130 --> 39:29.400
At the very least,

39:29.510 --> 39:31.010
he has to confess.

39:31.160 --> 39:31.930
Fine.

39:31.950 --> 39:32.530
Fine.

39:33.150 --> 39:34.510
I know what to do.

39:34.530 --> 39:35.250
Let me think about it.

39:35.990 --> 39:37.340
Let me see the baby.

39:39.450 --> 39:40.960
Is there such a thing now?

39:40.980 --> 39:42.090
It's at most a bud now.

39:42.160 --> 39:42.960
It's just a cell.

39:42.980 --> 39:43.830
Even if it's a cell,

39:43.830 --> 39:45.360
it's still the cutest little cell.
